"      </i>",
"      , 2007, 26(1):77-8.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"UTD.htm?31/3/31796/abstract-text/17195711/pubmed\" id=\"17195711\" target=\"_blank\">",
